    {
      "id": "standard_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "standard_0",
      "description": "This car is in poor condition. The exterior has multiple scratches, dents, and visible body damage. The interior is heavily worn with torn upholstery, damaged trim, and scuffed surfaces. The engine runs but has noticeable issues that will require attention. Best suited for buyers comfortable with a project vehicle or those seeking parts.",
